title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2010 SP2 VL Visio Project x86 - 03/2016
description:
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2010 SP2 VL Visio Project en-US 32-bit March 2016

Release Info

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Office ProPlus Version: 14.0.4755.1000
- Visio Premium version: 14.0.4763.1000
- Project Pro version: 14.0.4763.1000
- Spelling tools: English, French, Spanish

OS Requirements

- Windows XP with SP3 (excluding 64-bit editions)
- Windows Vista SP1 / 7 / 8 /10
- Windows Server 2003 with SP2 and MSXML 6.0 (excluding 64-bit edition)
- Windows Server 2003 R2 / 2008 / 2008 R2 / 2012

Includes

- Microsoft Office Professional Plus (Volume License) / Project Pro / Visio Pro (32-bit editions, en-US)
- Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (activator)
- Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required update)
- Optional: Classic Menu for Office v5.85, Office Tab v9.81

Integrated updates

Until March 8, 2016

Installation

- Mount / burn / extract and run Setup
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required, add-ins folder)
- Install any of these optional utilities (add-ins folder)

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 + serial
- Office Tab v9.81 + serial

Please don't be selfish and seed for a while ...
Thanks !
